{
   "strings":{
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_NAME":"Robomando",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_DESCRIPTION":"Your Robomando Model 7 is equipped with all of the tools necessary to salvage any mechanical device encountered in the wild.<color=#CCD3E0>\r\n\r\n< ! > His patented Re-Wire can co-op machines of any kind, even from a competitor!\r\n\r\n< ! > Built for speed, he is faster than most survivors on his feet, but isn't very durable. Use this speed to your advantage. It is generally more effective to run instead of trying to roll.\r\n\r\n< ! > While he himself may have weak damage, items that scale off of damage are generally stronger when used by Robomando. Use his re-wire to run through stages and quickly gain offensive items.\r\n\r\n< ! > Please keep in mind that, while your Robomando is equipped with offensive abilities, it is not designed for hostile environments\r\n\r\n

Translated by: Jaosnake",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_SUBTITLE":"Dinky Imitation",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_LORE":"I thought the advertisements were bogus at first. I mean, this little toy soldier is able to hack into any mechanical device? It sounded like bullshit.\r\n\r\nWell, imagine my shock when the thing hotwired my car and took it for a joyride. Found it two hours later totaled in a ditch. Apparently the thing couldn't reach the steering wheel.\r\n\r\nIt really just seemed like a toy to me. I hope to God no unaware parents got this little freak for their kids.\r\n\r\n",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_OUTRO_FLAVOR":"..and so it left nothing behind.",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_OUTRO_FAILURE":"..and so it failed, to no one's particular surprise or excitement.",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_MASTERY_SKIN_NAME":"Hero's Disciple",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_GRANDMASTERY_SKIN_NAME":"Trophy Taker",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_COMMANDO_SKIN_NAME":"Like Father, Like Son",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_BLUE_SKIN_NAME":"Soaked",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_GREEN_SKIN_NAME":"Goblin",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_SODA_SKIN_NAME":"Caffeinated Cretin",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_CLASSIC_SKIN_NAME":"Classic",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_PRIMARY_SHOT_NAME":"Single Fire",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_PRIMARY_SHOT_DESCRIPTION":"<style=cIsUtility>Agile.</style> Shoot for <style=cIsDamage>{0}% damage</style>.

Translated by: Jaosnake",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_SECONDARY_ZAP_NAME":"De-Escalate",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_SECONDARY_ZAP_DESCRIPTION":"<style=cIsUtility>Agile.</style> <style=cIsDamage>Stunning.</style> Fire a small, <style=cIsDamage>piercing</style> electric pulse for <style=cIsDamage>{0}% damage.

Translated by: Jaosnake",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_SECONDARY_BOMB_NAME":"Bouncy Bomb",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_SECONDARY_BOMB_DESCRIPTION":"Throw a bomb that bounces off of terrain and explodes on contact for <style=cIsDamage>{0}% damage.</style> Hold up to 2.

Translated by: Jaosnake",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_UTILITY_ROLL_NAME":"Evasive Maneuver",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_UTILITY_ROLL_DESCRIPTION":"Attempt to roll a short distance. <style=cIsUtility>You cannot be hit during the beginning of the roll.</style>

Translated by: Jaosnake",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_SPECIAL_HACK_NAME":"Re-Wire",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_SPECIAL_HACK_DESCRIPTION":"<style=cLunarObjective>Jury-Rig. </style>Re-wire a nearby mechanical object, <style=cIsUtility>activating it for free.</style>

Translated by: Jaosnake",
	  "RAT_ROBOMANDO_SPECIAL_OVERWIRE_NAME":"Over-Wire",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_SPECIAL_OVERWIRE_DESCRIPTION":"<style=cLunarObjective>Jury-Rig. </style>Re-wire a nearby mechanical object, <style=cIsUtility>activating it for free</style> with a<style=cIsUtility> {0}%</style> chance for <style=cIsUtility>enhanced output.</style>

Translated by: Jaosnake",
      "ACHIEVEMENT_RAT_ROBOMANDO_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME":"Robomando: Mastery",
      "ACHIEVEMENT_RAT_ROBOMANDO_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION":"As Robomando, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon.

Translated by: Jaosnake",
      "ACHIEVEMENT_RAT_ROBOMANDO_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME":"Robomando: Grandmastery",
      "ACHIEVEMENT_RAT_ROBOMANDO_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION":"As Robomando, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon or Eclipse (or higher).

Translated by: Jaosnake",
      "ACHIEVEMENT_RAT_ROBOMANDO_SODAACHIEVEMENT_NAME":"Robomando: Caffeine Addict",
      "ACHIEVEMENT_RAT_ROBOMANDO_SODAACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION":"As Robomando, hack a vending machine.

Translated by: Jaosnake",
      "RAT_ROBOMANDO_KEYWORD_JURY_RIG":"<style=cKeywordName>Jury-Rig</style><style=cSub>Re-wiring a printer will <style=cIsUtility>give you a scrap depending on the rarity of the printer item</style>, but <style=cDeath>destroys the printer.</style></style>"
